                          ==================
                          CDMS Collaboration
                          ==================
 
  History file for CDMS General Geometry cdms/cdmsim/CDMSgeometry
  ---------------------------------------------------------------

 This file should be used to summarize modifications and additions 
 made to the code and to keep track of all tags.

  ---------------------------------------------------------------
  * Please list in reverse chronological order (last date on top)
  ---------------------------------------------------------------
27 July 2011 Kevin McCarthy (MIT) (cdms-ggeom-V00-06-01)
-------------------------------------------------------
CDMS_GGSim now accepts a second argument that sets the run ID, 
for example, "CDMS_GGSim mymacro.mac <RunID>". 

22 July 2011 Michael Kelsey (SLAC) (cdms-ggeom-V00-06-00)
---------------------------------------------------------
Remove all local materials tables from construction classes; use new
singleton CDMSMaterialTable instead, which will be instantiated at the
beginning of the job.  This ensures that all materials are defined before
the NeutronHP process uses the materials DB to initialize cross-sections.

	detectors/CDMSMiniMaterials REMOVED
	detectors/ShieldMaterials REMOVED
	detectors/Am241SourceHolder
	detectors/CDMSMiniDetConstruction
	detectors/CDMSMultiTowerConstruction
	detectors/CDMSShieldConstruction
	detectors/CDMSTowerConstruction
	detectors/CDMSTowerSupportConstruction
	detectors/CDMSVesselConstruction
	detectors/CDMSZipConstruction
	detectors/CKGDetConstruction
	interface/CDMSGeomConstructor
	labs/NoLabMaterials REMOVED
	labs/SnoLabMaterials REMOVED
	labs/NoLab
	labs/SnoLab

- 7TowerSnoCosmic.mac, 7tower.mac, 9tower.mac, kgdet.mac:
  Follow change to CDMSRunActionMessenger.cc (cdms-actions-V00-02-03) which
  eliminated the /CDMS/Draw command.  

21 July 2011 Michael Kelsey (SLAC) (cdms-ggeom-V00-05-13)
---------------------------------------------------------
- zip+gammas.mac:  Add comment for Kevin's change below.

19 July 2011 Kevin McCarthy (MIT)
--------------------------------
- zip+gammas.mac:  Changed "AddLines" to "AddSpectrum" to agree with new
  CDMSMultiGenerator nomeclature

11 July 2011 Rudy Resch (SLAC) (cdms-ggeom-V00-05-12)
-----------------------------------------------------
- CDMSZipSD.cc:  Change sensitive detector to use pre step instead of post
  step.  Had some issues with energy depositions outside the crystal.

