4 May 2011  Michael Kelsey (SLAC) (cdms-ggeom-V00-04-12)
--------------------------------------------------------
- detectors/CDMSZipSD.cc: Use G4VTouchable to get transformation for hit
  coordinates; this provides directly world-to-local, instead of just
  mother-to-local.  Check name of post-step logical volume and reject hits
  which don't end inside a crystal ("LogicalZip").  Fix ctor constness.

- detectors/CDMSVetoSD.cc: Use G4VTouchable to get transformation for hit
  coordinates; this provides directly world-to-local, instead of just
  mother-to-local.  Fix ctor constness.

- detectors/CDMSZipHit, CDMSVetoHit:  Fix constness of SetTransform().

2 May 2011  Michael Kelsey (SLAC) (cdms-ggeom-V00-04-11)
--------------------------------------------------------
- detectors/CDMSZipConstruction:  Add G4bool "solid" flag to
  BuildHousingShape, so that mother volume is created all the way to r=0;
  otherwise ZIP placement is invalid, being "outside" the mother volume.

- detectors/CDMSTowerPattern.cc, Am241SourceHolder.cc:  Cast std::floor and
  std::ceil to G4int to avoid compiler warnings on Linux.

2 May 2011  Michael Kelsey (SLAC) (cdms-ggeom-V00-04-10)
--------------------------------------------------------
- CDMS_GGSim.cc:  Add QGSP_BERT_HP.hh for future testing.

- iZip100mm_Am241.mac, G101a.mac:  Refine ZIP and source parameters

- detectors/CDMS*Hit, CDMS*SD:  Change name of transform-setting function,
  add additional Z-offset for ZIP local coordinates.

- interface/CDMSGeomConstructor.cc:  Fix initialization order in ctor.

29 April 2011  Michael Kelsey (SLAC)
------------------------------------
- interface/CDMSGeomConstructor:  Move material table (CDMSVMaterials) to
  data member.  Materials must be pre-loaded in ctor in order for NeutronHP
  (used by Shielding physics list) to function properly.

29 April 2011  Michael Kelsey (SLAC) (cdms-ggeom-V00-04-08)
-----------------------------------------------------------
- Am241SourceHolder.cc:  Build canister as hollow cylinder, not solid (to
  avoid interspersed copper from placements).  Use collimator location as
  SourcePos, rather than center of source (for offset holes).

- iZip100mm_Am241.mac:  Change back to 1k events after finding bug in gamma
  generator.  Requires CDMSsources cdms-sources-V00-03-05.

28 April 2011  Michael Kelsey (SLAC) (cdms-ggeom-V00-04-07)
-----------------------------------------------------------
- bare-Am241holder.mac:  Add "DrawSolid" option to do opaque rendering.
- iZip100mm_Am241.mac:  Change to 100k events in order to get a few hits,
  set flag to use hardwired gamma lines.

- detectors/Am241SourceHolder.cc: Add recess to source puck, so that active
  source surface is exposed.  Use exponential based on activity to generate
  random time stamps.  Fix bug in SetSolidOrWireFrame() action.

27 April 2011  Michael Kelsey (SLAC) (cdms-ggeom-V00-04-06)
-----------------------------------------------------------
- detectors/CDMSZipHit, CDMSVetoHit:  Add coordinate transform from global
  to local ZIP coordinates, modify position accessors to apply transform.

- detectors/CDMSZipSD.cc, CDMSVetoSD.cc:  Set coordinate transformation from
  physical volume.

- detectors/Am241SourceHolder:  Use new Am241Lines class for hardwired
  gammas.  NOTE:  Requires CDMSsources cdms-sources-V00-03-04 or later.

- interface/Am241HolderMessenger:  Add selection of hardwired gammas.

- iZip100mm_Am241.mac:  Use hardwired gammas with source holder.

27 April 2011  Michael Kelsey (SLAC) (cdms-ggeom-V00-04-05)
-----------------------------------------------------------
- detectors/Am241SourceHolder:  Use new Messenger, add missing Set/Get
  functions for source activity, fix bug in atom-position generation.  Drop
  use of G4Region.  Add flag to draw object opaque vs. wire frame.

- interface/CDMSGeomMessenger:  Replace Am241Source with source-holder as
  real source; leave old version as "Am241toy".  Move GeometryManager to
  data member.

- interface/Am241HolderMessenger:  New class to interact with source holder.

22 April 2011  Michael Kelsey (SLAC) (cdms-ggeom-V00-04-04)
-----------------------------------------------------------
- detectors/Am241SourceHolder:  Change to subclass of CDMSVSourceConstruction:
  this makes it a "real source", and really should be in the CDMSsources
  package (which would lead to circular dependences).  Add full support for
  active sources in each canister, with Am-241 decays generated only in
  region close to the lead collimator.

22 April 2011  Michael Kelsey (SLAC)
------------------------------------
- detectors/Am241SourceHolder:  Add list of source names; create active
  Am-241 plug as daughter volume of source puck, and define a G4Region
  for use by actual source generator.  Change phi positions of canisters to
  match source layout drawing (engineering drawing is reversed).  Add some
  "tolerance" gaps between components to avoid geometry errors.

- bare-Am241holder.mac:  Change cutaway plane and viewpoint.
- overlaps_holder.mac:  Fix name of macro.

21 April 2011  Michael Kelsey (SLAC)
------------------------------------
- detectors/Am241SourceHolder.cc: Implement PrintParameters(), change phi
  positions of canisters to match drawing alignment with sides, corners.

- detectors/CDMSZipConstruction.cc: Change ZIP/housing clearance to 0.67 mm,
  fix bug in calculation of housing radius (should be dist to side, not to
  corner).

- bare-Am241holder.mac:  Add cutaway view of three sources.
- overlaps_holder.mac:  New geometry test of source holder.

21 April 2011  Michael Kelsey (SLAC) (cdms-ggeom-V00-04-03)
-----------------------------------------------------------
- G101a.mac:  Add configuration parameters for 100 mm ZIP with Y-flats.

- bare-Am241holder.mac:  New macro to draw "housing lid" plate and source
  holder for Am-241, used during G101 test run.

- iZip100mm_Am241.mac:  Add flats (only Y axis has them).

- detectors/Am241SourceHolder:  New class to define physical (mass) geometry
  for "housing lid" source holder.  Does not yet include active sources.
  The layout does not yet match the engineering drawings; this is a placeholder.

- interface/CDMSGeomMessenger.cc:  Add "holder" to Detector candidates to
  make drawing of new Am241SourceHolder.  Remove redundant #includes.

- interface/CDMSGeometryManager:  Add GetAm241Holder() accessor.
 
21 April 2011  Michael Kelsey (SLAC) (cdms-ggeom-V00-04-02)
