- G101a.mac:  New macro to be used for simulations of G101 (4" wafer) test.
  Derived from iZip100mm_Am241.mac with addition of flats and standoff of
  Am-241 plate from top of crystal.

- detectors/CDMSZipHit.hh, CDMSVetoHit.hh:  Make all GetXXX() accessors const.

