28 November 2010  Michael Kelsey (SLAC)
---------------------------------------
NOTE:  The current version of CDMSMultiTowerConstruction aborts during
BuildGeometry().  The abort is triggered in CDMSVesselConstruction because
some of the derived quantities are unfilled (zero).  All the subdetectors
need to be configured to fill and pass on their derived quantities before
the geometry phase begins.

