- create virtual class CDMSVSourceConstruction.hh.  It is a base class for
   the geometry construction of radiogenic and cosmogenic sources.  It 
   derives from the G4VUserPrimaryGeneratorAction class, thereby allowing 
   the active source position to be tied to the true geometrical position.

